of Public Health, as referenced by Alice M. Miller, &#8220;Sexual but Not Reproductive: Exploring the 
Junction and Disjunction of Sexual and Reproductive Rights&#8221;, in <i>Health and Human 
Rights</i> (2000), 4(2):68-109. 
<b>198
</b></p>
