Rwanda, E/CN.4/1998/54/Add.1; Indonesia and East Timor, E/CN.4/1999/68/Add.3; Cuba, 
E/CN.4/2000/68/Add.2; Pakistan and Afghanistan, E/CN.4/2000/68/Add.4; Bangladesh, Nepal 
